ed."],[2825,2887,"You."],[2962,3087,"It's why I came back."],[3125,3300,"It's why I hired you."],[3325,3437,"It's why I left tonight."],[3487,3625,"But I am going to prove"],[3625,3750,"how much you mean to me."],[3750,3875,"How much you've always meant."]],"63":[[666,779,"Hey, Rosie."],[879,962,"You're crying."],[962,1050,"Did he hurt you?"],[1225,1341,"Get on the next flight home."],[1366,1554,"You can't be alone on Christmas, Millie."],[2062,2166,"Oh, thank God."],[2212,2329,"I've been trying to call you."],[2375,2487,"My phone died on the plane."],[2487,2612,"Is everything okay?"],[2654,2754,"Is it Mom?"],[2775,2862,"It's Vicious."],[2954,3125,"Millie, his dad had a heart attack."],[3570,3737,"His father is dying."],[3804,3970,"Is this what he was trying to tell me?"],[4204,4404,"After all that we've been through,"],[4425,4650,"I still thought the worst of him."],[4779,4904,"I have to find him."],[5216,5329,"The clause in your father's will"],[5329,5416,"has been revoked."],[5425,5566,"The photos won't be released."],[5566,5741,"But I can't do anything about him"],[5741,5829,"writing you out."],[5862,5979,"I don't care about that."],[5979,6154,"Oh, and I heard Emilia"],[6154,6341,"landed in California an hour ago."],[6341,6416,"She's here?"],[6679,6741,"Emilia?"]],"64":[[195,283,"Vic."],[358,516,"I came as soon as I heard."],[608,804,"What do you want, Georgia?"],[916,1095,"I'm shocked to hear about your dad."],[1129,1291,"I know how much he meant to you."],[1366,1554,"You have no idea"],[1554,1670,"what he means to me."],[1670,1795,"What he did to me."],[1841,2004,"Emilia's the only one who knows."],[2029,2120,"Who cares."],[2158,2279,"At least I thought she did."],[2383,2516,"You can show yourself out."],[2545,2729,"Oh, but I can make you"],[2729,2841,"feel so much better."],[3008,3220,"I should have given him a chance."],[3258,3416,"Is he all alone just"],[3416,3533,"waiting for me to-"],[3533,3604,"Baby."],[3983,4158,"We always fuck when you're in town."]],"