et it."],[5229,5279,"Do it!"],[5279,5379,"No, you don't!"],[5379,5587,"You don't fucking get it!"],[5729,5929,"You treat everyone like a pawn"],[5929,6000,"in your games"],[6000,6279,"but I am so tired of"],[6279,6462,"getting played with, Vicious!"],[6754,7012,"I am not playing fucking games"],[7012,7116,"with you, Emilia."],[7116,7429,"When I play games, I don't fucking lose!"],[7450,7537,"I'm not letting you go"],[7554,7704,"until you let me tell you the truth."]],"67":[[25,129,"When I got the call about my dad,"],[129,337,"I was so fucking angry!"],[400,529,"I couldn't think straight."],[629,704,"My lawyer called"],[737,800,"and he told me that"],[800,904,"he's trying to write me out of the will,"],[904,962,"and I am-"],[962,1091,"So this is about money?"],[1204,1404,"Don't you think that you have enough?"],[1404,1516,"No, no, you don't understand."],[1516,1591,"This isn't about money."],[1591,1766,"Oh, then is it about hurting me?"],[1766,1954,"You sleep with me, finally,"],[1954,2191,"and then you go and fuck the one person"],[2191,2304,"who hated me more than you"],[2304,2391,"since high school."],[2466,2600,"Are you punishing me?"],[2629,2679,"No."],[2679,2854,"For, for knocking your walls down,"],[2854,3079,"for seeing you for who you really are?"],[3079,3362,"You aren't fucking seeing me, Emilia!"],[3441,3562,"You're not trusting me!"],[3562,3662,"Do you really think"],[3662,3804,"that you deserve my trust?"],[3891,3962,"You're right."],[4025,4116,"You're right, okay?"],[4141,4337,"I know that I'm fucked up,"],[4375,4600,"but I am not asking you to fix me!"]],"68":[[4,204,"Then what are you asking me, Vicious?"],[487,600,"Are you giving up on me?"],[687,754,"On us?"],[862,1037,"We are not good for each other."],[1316,1391,"I used to think"],[1391,1516,"that you were the villain,"],[1725,1941,"but you're not my villain."],[2091,2191,"You're your own."],[2300,2587,"You are just a lesson to me."],[2629,2987,"An important, brutal lesson."],[3162,3362,"Nothing 