 is taking every ounce"],[483,595,"of fucking willpower"],[595,700,"I have not to."],[862,937,"But I want you to know"],[937,1050,"how serious I am about you."],[1133,1212,"About us."],[1287,1358,"Vicious."],[2687,2825,"Will you let me take you to lunch?"],[2975,3062,"Just lunch."],[3087,3162,"No catch."],[3208,3287,"Fine."],[3508,3608,"Now be a good girl."],[3737,3812,"And go home."],[4454,4520,"Come on."],[5212,5425,"He's never been so sweet."],[5470,5620,"Part of me wants to believe it,"],[5620,5825,"but the other part..."],[6112,6175,"Mom?"],[6245,6312,"What's wrong?"],[6345,6445,"We've been kicked out of"],[6445,6525,"our apartment."],[6625,6725,"I've been fired."],[6783,6850,"Fired?"],[6850,6912,"Why?"],[6958,7075,"Vicious, Millie."],[7162,7262,"He did this."]],"74":[[4,112,"His dad is dying"],[112,312,"and he has full control of the estate."],[312,500,"I knew this family would find a way"],[500,700,"to screw us over again."],[700,816,"It's what they do."],[929,1054,"We're never gonna be free of them"],[1054,1254,"until we get out of this place for good."],[1266,1454,"Mom, I was just with Vicious."],[1491,1616,"There's no way that he..."],[1716,2025,"When I play games, I don't fucking lose!"],[2054,2154,"He wouldn't play games"],[2154,2279,"like this with me again."],[2366,2441,"Would he?"],[2516,2662,"I'll talk to him, okay?"],[2679,2829,"We know how this ends."],[2891,2991,"He wins."],[3029,3379,"Maybe, but I need to hear it from him."],[3862,3941,"Vicious!"],[4712,4816,"Emilia."],[4995,5108,"You're never far"],[5108,5254,"when Vicious is around."],[5325,5533,"Like a sad"],[5595,5683,"little"],[5712,5829,"stray"],[5920,6000,"dog."]],"75":[[0,162,"Henry, where's Vicious?"],[162,350,"It's Mr. Spencer to you."],[462,575,"And if you don't know,"],[575,758,"he must be playing you too."],[825,1008,"What are you talking about?"],[1033,1258,"You know, I almost feel sorry for you."],[1312,1445,"A decade later"],[1445,1737,"and he's still pulling your strings?"],[1762,2170,"Women like you are so dazzled by money"],[2170,2337,"you don't even notice"],[2337,2483,"when you're being used"],[2483,2862,"until it's all used up."],[2887,2962,"You know that's why"],[2962,3020,"I had to stop"],[3020,3150,"fucking your mother, right?"],[3150,3387,"All the light had gone out of her eyes."],[3387,3612,"Don't fucking talk about my mother!"],[3745,3983,"Hey, I don't have any reason to anymore."],[4037,4250,"I had my attorney fire her this morning."],[4320,4450,"You fired her?"],[4575,4645,"Why?"],[4645,4850,"Because whatever stunt this is"],[4850,4962,"Vicious is pulling, he..."],[5070,5370,"He signed the deed to the mansion"],[5370,5500,"over to your mother"],[5500,5808,"before I even had a chance to die."],[5850,6033,"Vicious gave the property to us?"],[6150,6225,"Why?"],[6250,6358,"I don't know."],[6437,6537,"And I don't care."],[6562,6737,"If you think I'm gonna"],[6737,7037,"let your whore of a mother"],[7037,7237,"take my house,"],[7237,7545,"then you're as stupid as you look."],[7545,7775,"I don't care if I'm dying."],[7775,7912,"I'm not giving your"],[7912,8262,"fucking pathetic family a penny."]],"76":[[33,150,"My family is better"],[150,287,"than yours will ever be."],[412,475,"At least we're not"],[475,612,"a bunch of crazy vultures"],[612,775,"that only fight over money."],[800,970,"That's because you don't have any."],[1000,1108,"Do you really think"],[1108,1258,"that we want this place?"],[1425,1733,"It's ugly, cold, and miserable"],[1733,1850,"just like you."],[1900,2070,"Well if that's what you think,"],[2133,2262,"then you won't mind"],[2262,2612,"watching it all go up in flames."],[3158,3283,"What are you doing?"],[3295,3475,"I'm not letting you or Vicious win."],[3550,3625,"Why are you"],[3625,3787,"so obsessed with winning?"],[3812,3950,"Oh no sweetheart."],[3950,4095,"We're not going anywhere."],[4112,4287,"Vicious staged all this."],[4287,4600,"So now he can watch us all burn."],[4600,4750,"Let me go!"],[4750,4850,"Viciou